Package: rhealpix
Type: Package
Title: Implementation of the Healpix pixelization scheme
Version: 1.0
Date: 2011-01-25
Author: Maurizio Tomasi
Maintainer: Maurizio Tomasi <maurizio.tomasi@unimi.it>
Description: This package provides a implementation in pure R of the Healpix
	     pixelization routine as described by Gorski et al. (2003) and
	     implemented by the Healpix package. It has a number of utilities
             for needlet calculation as well.
Depends: rfitsio
License: GPL-2
LazyLoad: yes
